@startuml Auth_Random_FSM

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor LightGreen
    BorderColor DarkGreen
    FontSize 12
}

title Random Generator (auth_random) - Counter/LFSR Sequencer

[*] --> READY : rst

state READY : ready=1\nvalid=0\nbusy=0\nwait load
state MIXING : ready=0\nvalid=0\nbusy=1\nadvance LFSR each cycle\nincrement counter
state DONE_PULSE : valid=1 (if busy)\nready=1\nbusy=0\ncounter reset

READY --> MIXING : load\nstate<=seed ^ state\ncounter=0
MIXING --> DONE_PULSE : counter == 16
DONE_PULSE --> READY : next cycle

note right of MIXING
  Internal implementation is a single always_ff
  process with busy/counter as phase control.
  This diagram shows the equivalent FSM view.
end note

@enduml
